  you are in love with Mazie.

07:19.706 --> 07:22.541
   It ain't a thinking matter
    Mrs. Wales, I know I am.

07:26.747 --> 07:27.379
           Listen Jim,

07:27.380 --> 07:28.012
 I don't think it's for the best

07:28.015 --> 07:30.182
       that you and Mazie
        see one another.

07:37.624 --> 07:38.824
    [Peaches] What the hell?

07:38.826 --> 07:41.092
      Who's that layin' up
      in your best, Buster?

07:41.094 --> 07:44.529
   Look, he's got his fucking
      shoes on in my bed.

07:44.531 --> 07:47.833
   You keep your goddamn dirty
   clodhoppers off my sheets.

07:47.835 --> 07:49.167
            (laughs)

07:49.169 --> 07:50.602
      Hey, what's the idea?

07:50.604 --> 07:53.038
     The clerk feller told
     me to take bunk three.

07:53.040 --> 07:54.973
   That queer don't know shit.

07:54.975 --> 07:59.044
  This boll-weevil must be one
   of them college athletes.

07:59.046 --> 08:01.613
     He looks like a little
     two-bit hotshot to me.

08:02.883 --> 08:03.982
        Ain't that right?

08:05.619 --> 08:07.252
        Hotshot, you got
       dirt in those ears?

08:07.254 --> 08:09.221
        [Jim] I answer to
        the name McNeely.

08:10.991 --> 08:13.058
   [Buster] Know your goddamn
     place, you stay down.

08:13.060 --> 08:14.660
          Get off him.

08:14.661 --> 08:16.261
       [Buster] You leave
     this bunk be, hotshot.

08:22.069 --> 08:23.001
             Go on.

08:25.939 --> 08:27.639
            Assholes.

08:27.641 --> 08:30.709
       (soft violin tones)

08:31.078 --> 08:32.143
     (rock hits sheet metal)

08:42.655 --> 08:44.523
       [Jim] I got plans.

08:44.525 --> 08:46.691
        [Mrs. Wales] Face
         the facts, Jim.

08:47.928 --> 08:49.794
      You're a checker in a
    grocery store and that is

08:49.796 --> 08:53.198
     all you're equipped by
 background or education to be.

08:53.200 --> 08:54.867
         Piece of shit.

08:54.868 --> 08:56.535
      [Mrs. Wales] I want
     you to see my husband.

08:57.538 --> 08:59.271
    He has important friends,

08:59.273 --> 09:01.273
         he'll get you a
       good job somewhere.

09:02.976 --> 09:05.010
 Perhaps out in the oil fields.

09:05.012 --> 09:06.011
            (screams)

09:08.282 --> 09:12.017
  (anxious music chord rising)

09:12.019 --> 09:15.220
         (men grunting)

09:23.997 --> 09:24.930
              Ort!

09:25.832 --> 09:26.998
      Take that boll-weevil

09:27.000 --> 09:29.801
     and get to piss-antin'
          them joints.

09:30.837 --> 09:33.004
       By God, you'd best
         keep up today.

09:36.209 --> 09:39.210
     Just hook your hand in
     the belt, do like I do.

09:39.212 --> 09:42.347
        When I say hump,
    heister-up and take off.

09:42.349 --> 09:44.683
Ain't nothin' but back and guts.

09:44.685 --> 09:46.284
           All right.
           Here we go.

09:46.286 --> 09:47.152
              Hump.

09:47.154 --> 09:48.286
            (grunts)

09:48.288 --> 09:49.354
           Step back!

09:53.360 --> 09:54.826
