        his fucking head.

09:57.364 --> 09:59.297
     Why don't you go ahead
     and check him, Peaches?

10:01.301 --> 10:03.368
        Goddamn you sorry
        ass boll-weevil.

10:03.370 --> 10:06.771
       Are you trying to
      get somebody killed?

10:14.081 --> 10:15.013
            (grunts)

10:20.354 --> 10:21.286
