11:35.862 --> 11:39.164
     (relaxed violin music)

12:06.993 --> 12:09.194
   Move your ass, boll-weevil.

12:15.068 --> 12:16.267
         [Ort] Come on.

12:16.269 --> 12:17.268
            Come on.

12:17.270 --> 12:19.404
          There ya go.

12:19.406 --> 12:21.439
       All right everybody
          up, let's go.

12:25.378 --> 12:29.347
 (relaxed country guitar music)

12:58.411 --> 13:01.246
        [Cap] All right,
        that's breeeeak!

13:03.950 --> 13:05.850
     Yeah, not you McNeely.

13:08.488 --> 13:11.956
     (relaxed violin music)

13:47.360 --> 13:49.561
      Been expecting you,
     just didn't know when.

13:50.864 --> 13:52.397
            You win.

13:52.399 --> 13:54.599
