13:54.601 --> 13:57.335
          You said it,
      nothing here for me.

13:57.337 --> 13:58.653
          [Dent] Look.

13:58.654 --> 13:59.970
 Personally I don't give a damn.

13:59.973 --> 14:02.941
         It's completely
        immaterial to me.

14:02.943 --> 14:04.609
       But I hate to give
       those Neanderthal

14:04.611 --> 14:06.544
      bastards the pleasure
       of running you off.

14:06.546 --> 14:07.946
         I can't do it.

14:07.948 --> 14:09.614
      [Dent] You came here
    with something to prove.

14:10.951 --> 14:13.418
     Now I don't know to who

14:13.420 --> 14:15.086
     but I do see it in you.

14:17.490 --> 14:18.423
           Besides...

14:19.926 --> 14:21.926
         you don't have
     anything to go back to.

14:29.069 --> 14:30.268
            Sit down.

14:50.957 --> 14:52.557
       Can I get a raise?

14:52.559 --> 14:55.026
         (Dent chuckles)

14:55.028 --> 14:59.230
       (slow tempo country
          guitar tones)

