        (horse neighing)

18:27.774 --> 18:29.841
    Oh Lord, here she comes.

18:31.411 --> 18:32.877
            Hi Dent.
             Ma'am.

18:35.248 --> 18:37.148
   Hey ma'am, what can I get?

18:37.150 --> 18:40.651
     Boy, I am in love with
     that engineer's wife.

18:40.653 --> 18:42.587
 You are just a randy old goat,

