18:59.272 --> 19:01.606
        [Jim] She sure is
      something to look at.

19:01.608 --> 19:04.142
     Yeah but lookin' at it
  ain't getting it, now is it?

19:04.144 --> 19:05.543
    Which reminds me fellas,

19:05.545 --> 19:08.212
      I got some business
     to transact in Odessa.

19:08.214 --> 19:10.515
      Take the strain off.

19:10.517 --> 19:11.449
             Adios.

