   so far from the other rigs?

19:54.526 --> 19:56.593
   [Barry] I'm seeing if this
   wildcat's worth drilling.

19:56.596 --> 19:57.828
        The damn lease is
        about to expire,

19:57.830 --> 19:59.597
      so I gotta see what's
      going on underneath.

19:59.599 --> 20:02.833
   I'm a geologist for Bison,
      name's Barry Wakely.

20:02.835 --> 20:04.302
             Barry,

20:04.304 --> 20:05.636
        Jim, Jim McNeely.

20:06.673 --> 20:08.539
      We cut the damn hole.

