    [Jim] Ever thought about
     going out on your own?

20:43.476 --> 20:44.675
     I've thought about it.

20:46.679 --> 20:48.279
         Well if you run
       across an oil field

20:48.281 --> 20:51.315
    nobody's found yet, maybe
     you and I can grab it.

20:51.317 --> 20:51.949
          Coker field.

20:53.753 --> 20:56.287
        As in Coker City?

20:56.289 --> 20:58.422
         The old codger
       won't lease it out.

