      Convince him and your
       name will be known

21:00.560 --> 21:03.494
   for 14 counties, hell maybe
  all the way up to Fort Worth.

21:04.497 --> 21:05.896
 A couple broke bastards like us

21:05.898 --> 21:07.632
can't compete with the big boys.

21:08.768 --> 21:10.768
       Good thing I enjoy
      sniffin' them rocks.

21:13.039 --> 21:13.971
           (chuckles)

21:20.480 --> 21:21.912
        That damn Pluto's
         as worthless as

21:21.914 --> 21:24.915
     a one-legged man in an
      ass kicking contest.

21:24.917 --> 21:26.817
        Spent the entire
        day behind a bush

21:26.819 --> 21:29.420
       and Cap didn't do a
     goddamn thing about it.

21:29.422 --> 21:31.472
         Why should he?

21:31.473 --> 21:33.523
     He's the nephew of the
    Vice-President of Bison.

21:33.526 --> 21:35.326
          A blue blood
      through and through.

21:37.697 --> 21:41.032
      The luck lands on the
 sorriest, most worthless souls.

21:41.034 --> 21:42.833
Good work out there today, boys.

21:43.703 --> 21:44.869
      How much we got now?

21:45.905 --> 21:47.538
           I've got..

21:47.540 --> 21:51.042
             $3,221.

21:51.044 --> 21:52.443
              Oou.

21:52.445 --> 21:53.678
       Tell you what let's
       do, let's take that

21:53.680 --> 21:57.448
       3,221 and let's go
       down to old Mexico.

21:57.450 --> 22:00.484
  We'll get us a big old house
 with plenty of tequila and some

22:00.486 --> 22:03.721
   cute little muchachos and
   man, we'll have us a time.

22:03.723 --> 22:05.089
   And when we're cashed out?

22:05.091 --> 22:07.892
        Well then we come
      back here and save up

22:07.894 --> 22:11.395
      another 3,221 and do
       it all over again.

22:11.397 --> 22:13.097
       Oh goddamn, I like
        the sound of it.

22:13.099 --> 22:14.665
      It sure sounds sweet.

22:16.769 --> 22:19.437
     This here is my ticket
      outta here, fellas.

22:20.540 --> 22:24.375
