        ¶ Hello, hello ¶

50:26.657 --> 50:31.727
        ¶ How'd things go
         for you today ¶

50:32.430 --> 50:36.065
     ¶ Don't you miss her ¶

50:36.067 --> 50:40.803
¶ Since she up and walked away ¶

50:40.805 --> 50:44.673
       ¶ And I'll bet you
        dread to spend ¶

50:44.675 --> 50:49.712
¶ Another lonely night with me ¶

50:50.782 --> 50:55.284
       ¶ But lonely walls,
     I'll keep you company ¶

50:57.622 --> 50:58.487
              Ted.

50:58.489 --> 50:59.722
        ¶ Hello window ¶

50:59.724 --> 51:01.824
        ¶ Hello, hello ¶

